{"type":"message","id":"6ea2d132","parentId":"0c8450d1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:00:08.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is asking for Telugu movie recommendations available on OTT platforms for the weekend. Let me search for current good Telugu movies on OTT.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Great pick for the weekend @Sravya! Here are some good Telugu movies currently on OTT:\n\n**🔥 Must Watch:**\n\n🎬 **Kalki 2898 AD** — *Prime Video*\n• Prabhas, Deepika, Amitabh Bachchan\n• Sci-fi mythology epic. Visual spectacle!\n\n🎬 **HanuMan** — *ZEE5*\n• Teja Sajja\n• Superhero + Indian mythology. Surprisingly good!\n\n🎬 **Tillu Square** — *Netflix*\n• Siddhu Jonnalagadda\n• Comedy crime thriller. Hilarious & stylish.\n\n🎬 **Ambajipeta Marriage Band** — *Prime Video*\n• Suhas\n• Feel-good village drama. Beautiful storytelling.\n\n🎬 **Gaami** — *ZEE5*\n• Vishwak Sen\n• Unique thriller with great visuals. Different from usual stuff.\n\n**🎭 Underrated Picks:**\n\n🎬 **Om Bheem Bush** — *Netflix*\n• Sree Vishnu\n• Comedy with heart. Great for laughs.\n\n🎬 **Sundaram Master** — *Prime Video*\n• Harsha Chemudu\n• Light-hearted entertainer.\n\n🎬 **Chandramukhi 2** — *Prime Video*\n• Horror comedy vibes. Fun watch.\n\n**Quick picks by mood:**\n• Want action epic? → **Kalki 2898 AD** 🏹\n• Want laughs? → **Tillu Square** or **Om Bheem Bush** 😂\n• Want something different? → **Gaami** 🧠\n• Want feel-good? → **Ambajipeta Marriage Band** 💛\n\nWhat's your vibe @Sravya? I can narrow it down further! ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":450,"output":432,"cacheRead":42432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774717197186}}
