or suspense movies"}],"timestamp":1774717453587}}
{"type":"message","id":"4755388d","parentId":"779d2c8f","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:04:23.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya wants comedy, horror, or suspense Telugu movies on OTT. Let me give focused recommendations for each genre.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here you go @Sravya! Genre-wise picks 👇\n\n**😂 Comedy:**\n\n🎬 **Tillu Square** — *Netflix*\n• Comedy crime. Witty dialogues, great timing. Top pick!\n\n🎬 **Om Bheem Bush** — *Netflix*\n• Sree Vishnu comedy. Laugh-out-loud moments.\n\n🎬 **MAD** — *Netflix*\n• College comedy. Fun & nostalgic vibes.\n\n🎬 **Samajavaragamana** — *Aha*\n• Clean family comedy. Light & entertaining.\n\n**👻 Horror:**\n\n🎬 **Virupaksha** — *Netflix*\n• Sai Dharam Tej. Genuinely scary with a solid story.\n\n🎬 **Masooda** — *Aha*\n• Indie horror. Low budget but really effective scares.\n\n🎬 **Chandramukhi 2** — *Prime Video*\n• Horror comedy. Entertaining if you liked the original.\n\n**🔍 Suspense/Thriller:**\n\n🎬 **HIT: The 2nd Case** — *Prime Video*\n• Adivi Sesh. Gripping crime thriller. Edge-of-seat stuff.\n\n🎬 **Gaami** — *ZEE5*\n• Unique suspense with great twists. Keeps you guessing.\n\n🎬 **Ante Sundaraniki** — *Netflix*\n• Not pure suspense but has unexpected turns. Rom-com with depth.\n\n🎬 **Evaru** — *Prime Video*\n• Adivi Sesh. Whodunit thriller. One of the best!\n\n**🏆 My top 3 for you:**\n1. **Tillu Square** (comedy) — guaranteed fun\n2. **Virupaksha** (horror) — actually scary\n3. **Evaru** (suspense) — mind-blowing twists\n\nPick your poison @Sravya! 🎬⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1059,"output":439,"cacheRead":42816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774717453589}}
