! 🎬⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nI have already seen these movies\nTell me another set of mvis"}],"timestamp":1774717606156}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f9a7258","parentId":"3df6d34a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:06:57.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya has already seen all those movies and wants more recommendations. Let me think of more Telugu movies on OTT platforms that I haven't mentioned yet.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Oh you're a movie buff @Sravya! Let me dig deeper 🎬\n\n**😂 Comedy (Hidden gems):**\n\n🎬 **Balagam** — *Prime Video*\n• Village drama with dark comedy. Beautiful & emotional.\n\n🎬 **Miss Shetty Mr Polishetty** — *Netflix*\n• Anushka + Naveen. Sweet rom-com with great chemistry.\n\n🎬 **Writer Padmabhushan** — *Prime Video*\n• Suhas. Quirky comedy about a struggling writer.\n\n🎬 **Geethanjali Malli Vachindi** — *Prime Video*\n• Horror comedy sequel. Fun popcorn watch.\n\n**👻 Horror (Lesser known):**\n\n🎬 **Bhaag Saale** — *Prime Video*\n• Horror comedy. Underrated entertainer.\n\n🎬 **Maa Oori Polimera** — *Aha*\n• Rural horror thriller. Different vibe, genuinely creepy.\n\n🎬 **Arundhati** — *Hotstar*\n• Classic but if you haven't seen it — Anushka's best horror. Iconic!\n\n**🔍 Suspense/Thriller (Deep cuts):**\n\n🎬 **Agent Sai Srinivasa Athreya** — *Prime Video*\n• Naveen Polishetty. Comedy + mystery. Brilliant writing!\n\n🎬 **Goodachari** — *Prime Video*\n• Adivi Sesh. Spy thriller. Fast-paced & gripping.\n\n🎬 **HIT (1st Case)** — *Prime Video*\n• If you've only seen the 2nd one. Vishwak Sen kills it.\n\n🎬 **Brochevarevarura** — *Prime Video*\n• Sree Vishnu. Dark comedy thriller. Twists you won't see coming.\n\n🎬 **Mathu Vadalara** — *Netflix*\n• Unique comedy-thriller. Fresh concept, great execution.\n\n🎬 **C/o Kancharapalem** — *Netflix*\n• Anthology drama. Not thriller but deeply moving. Masterpiece if you haven't seen it.\n\n**🏆 Fresh top 3:**\n1. **Agent Sai Srinivasa Athreya** — comedy + mystery perfection\n2. **Mathu Vadalara** — wildly unique\n3. **Balagam** — emotional powerhouse\n\nHow many of these have you seen @Sravya? 😂 Let's find ones you HAVEN'T watched! ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1063,"output":560,"cacheRead":43840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774717606158}}
