Netflix\\n• Unique comedy-thriller. Fresh concept, great execution.\\n\\n🎬 C/o Kancharapalem — Netflix\\n• Anthology drama. Not thriller but deeply moving. Masterpiece if you haven't seen it.\\n\\n🏆 Fresh top 3:\\n\\n1. Agent Sai Srinivasa Athreya — comedy + mystery perfection\\n2. Mathu Vadalara — wildly unique\\n3. Balagam — emotional powerhouse\\n\\nHow many of these have you seen @Sravya? 😂 Let's find ones you HAVEN'T watched! ⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nThese are all old mvis and i have already watched"}],"timestamp":1774717683511}}
