{"type":"message","id":"9f3584b6","parentId":"b18b8965","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:08:18.095Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_93a1da90a602439c88942b40","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"latest Telugu movies OTT 2026 new releases Netflix Prime Video\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 7113,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6a68b5eb4c8f18be\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAs of March 28, 2026, several new Telugu movies have been released or are slated for release on Netflix and Amazon Prime Video.\\n\\n**Netflix New Releases & Upcoming Telugu Movies 2026:**\\n\\n*   **Funky**: This romantic entertainer, starring Vishwak Sen, began streaming on Netflix from March 13, 2026, in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi, following its theatrical release.\\n*   **With Love**: After its theatrical release on February 6, 2026, this romantic drama became available on Netflix from March 6, 2026, in multiple languages including Telugu, Tamil, Hindi, Malayalam, and Kannada.\\n\\nNetflix has also announced a significant Telugu film slate for 2026, referred to as \\\"Netflix Pandaga,\\\" which includes a mix of mainstream entertainers and character-driven films. These titles are expected to stream on the platform after their theatrical runs:\\n\\n*   **Ustaad Bhagat Singh**: Featuring Pawan Kalyan, Sreeleela, and Raashi Khanna.\\n*   **Peddi**: A sports action drama starring Ram Charan and Janhvi Kapoor.\\n*   **The Paradise**: A darker film with Nani.\\n*   **Adarsha Kutumbam – House No: 47**: Starring Venkatesh.\\n*   **VD14**: A period-action project with Vijay Deverakonda.\\n*   **Aakasamlo Oka Tara**: Featuring Dulquer Salmaan.\\n*   **Don't Trouble the Trouble**: Led by Fahadh Faasil.\\n*   **Biker**: Starring Sharwanand, Rajasekhar, and Malvika Nair.\\n*   **Production No 37**.\\n*   **Champion**: With Roshan Meka.\\n*   **418**.\\n*   **Raakaasa**.\\n*   **Takshakudu**.\\n*   **Super Subbu**.\\n*   **Legacy**.\\n\\n**Amazon Prime Video New Releases & Upcoming Telugu Movies 2026:**\\n\\n*   **Vishnu Vinyasam**: Sree Vishnu's romantic comedy entertainer, released in theaters on February 27, 2026, made its digital debut on Amazon Prime Video starting March 20, 2026.\\n*   **Couple Friendly (Telugu)**: This romance drama, starring Santosh Soban and Manasa Varanasi, is available on Prime Video and is listed as a 2026 release.\\n\\nAmazon Prime Video has also unveiled its 2026 post-theatrical streaming slate, which includes:\\n\\n*   **Goodachari 2**: Starring Adivi Sesh.\\n*   **Vvan**: Featuring Sidharth Malhotra and Tamannaah Bhatia.\\n*   **Naagzilla**: With Kartik Aaryan.\\n*   **DQ41**: Starring Dulquer Salmaan and Pooja Hegde.\\n*   **Mirzapur The Film**: Featuring a large ensemble cast including Ali Fazal and Pankaj Tripathi.\\n*   **O'Romeo**: With Shahid Kapoor and Triptii Dimri.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6a68b5eb4c8f18be\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.filmibeat.com/top-listing/new-ott-releases-this-week-in-telugu-2026-aha-prime-video-netflix-zee5-hotstar-sunnxt-and-sonyliv-6-1079.html\",\n      \"title\": \"filmibeat.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/regional-cinema/story/netflix-locks-big-telugu-releases-for-2026-from-pawan-kalyan-to-ram-charan-2853201-2026-01-16\",\n      \"title\": \"indiatoday.in\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.123telugu.com/mnews/ott-netflix-announces-2026-telugu-movie-slate-on-sankranthi-peddi-ustaad-bhagat-singh-the-paradise-adarsha-kutumbam-more-prp.html\",\n      \"title\": \"123telugu.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.indiatvnews.com/entertainment/ott/netflix-pandaga-2026-telugu-movies-list-2026-01-16-1026176\",\n      \"title\": \"indiatvnews.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/coming-soon/netflix-india-announces-new-tamil-telugu-originals-for-release-in-2026/\",\n      \"title\": \"whats-on-netflix.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.primevideo.com/detail/Couple-Friendly-Telugu/0PZ8BT07CJIHUYCKBJ4HAJ8FL1\",\n      \"title\": \"primevideo.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.123telugu.com/mnews/ott-amazon-prime-video-unveils-2026-post-theatrical-streaming-slate-goodachari-2-naagzilla-vvan-more-prp.html\",\n      \"title\": \"123telugu.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"latest Telugu movies OTT 2026 new releases Netflix Prime Video","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":7113,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6a68b5eb4c8f18be\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAs of March 28, 2026, several new Telugu movies have been released or are slated for release on Netflix and Amazon Prime Video.\n\n**Netflix New Releases & Upcoming Telugu Movies 2026:**\n\n*   **Funky**: This romantic entertainer, starring Vishwak Sen, began streaming on Netflix from March 13, 2026, in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi, following its theatrical release.\n*   **With Love**: After its theatrical release on February 6, 2026, this romantic drama became available on Netflix from March 6, 2026, in multiple languages including Telugu, Tamil, Hindi, Malayalam, and Kannada.\n\nNetflix has also announced a significant Telugu film slate for 2026, referred to as \"Netflix Pandaga,\" which includes a mix of mainstream entertainers and character-driven films. These titles are expected to stream on the platform after their theatrical runs:\n\n*   **Ustaad Bhagat Singh**: Featuring Pawan Kalyan, Sreeleela, and Raashi Khanna.\n*   **Peddi**: A sports action drama starring Ram Charan and Janhvi Kapoor.\n*   **The Paradise**: A darker film with Nani.\n*   **Adarsha Kutumbam – House No: 47**: Starring Venkatesh.\n*   **VD14**: A period-action project with Vijay Deverakonda.\n*   **Aakasamlo Oka Tara**: Featuring Dulquer Salmaan.\n*   **Don't Trouble the Trouble**: Led by Fahadh Faasil.\n*   **Biker**: Starring Sharwanand, Rajasekhar, and Malvika Nair.\n*   **Production No 37**.\n*   **Champion**: With Roshan Meka.\n*   **418**.\n*   **Raakaasa**.\n*   **Takshakudu**.\n*   **Super Subbu**.\n*   **Legacy**.\n\n**Amazon Prime Video New Releases & Upcoming Telugu Movies 2026:**\n\n*   **Vishnu Vinyasam**: Sree Vishnu's romantic comedy entertainer, released in theaters on February 27, 2026, made its digital debut on Amazon Prime Video starting March 20, 2026.\n*   **Couple Friendly (Telugu)**: This romance drama, starring Santosh Soban and Manasa Varanasi, is available on Prime Video and is listed as a 2026 release.\n\nAmazon Prime Video has also unveiled its 2026 post-theatrical streaming slate, which includes:\n\n*   **Goodachari 2**: Starring Adivi Sesh.\n*   **Vvan**: Featuring Sidharth Malhotra and Tamannaah Bhatia.\n*   **Naagzilla**: With Kartik Aaryan.\n*   **DQ41**: Starring Dulquer Salmaan and Pooja Hegde.\n*   **Mirzapur The Film**: Featuring a large ensemble cast including Ali Fazal and Pankaj Tripathi.\n*   **O'Romeo**: With Shahid Kapoor and Triptii Dimri.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6a68b5eb4c8f18be\">>>","citations":[{"url":"https://www.filmibeat.com/top-listing/new-ott-releases-this-week-in-telugu-2026-aha-prime-video-netflix-zee5-hotstar-sunnxt-and-sonyliv-6-1079.html","title":"filmibeat.com"},{"url":"https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/regional-cinema/story/netflix-locks-big-telugu-releases-for-2026-from-pawan-kalyan-to-ram-charan-2853201-2026-01-16","title":"indiatoday.in"},{"url":"https://www.123telugu.com/mnews/ott-netflix-announces-2026-telugu-movie-slate-on-sankranthi-peddi-ustaad-bhagat-singh-the-paradise-adarsha-kutumbam-more-prp.html","t