{"type":"message","id":"d8743a29","parentId":"fb1015c4","timestamp":"2026-03-28T19:11:28.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Oh, he's asking about a body part. If someone is lying on someone's lap and looking up at their face... the answer would be the nose (if she's looking down) or... well, he said \"naughty\" so he's probably fishing for a cheeky answer. But I'll keep it clean and answer naturally - the nose or chin would be the body part between your eyes and her face if she's looking down at you. Or maybe he's thinking of something else entirely.\n\nLet me just give the straightforward answer - her nose comes between your eyes and her face if she's looking down. I'll keep it light.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Her nose 😂\n\nIf she's looking down at you and you're looking up at her, her nose is literally what's in between your line of sight to her face.\n\nThat's it? That's the \"naughty\" question? 😂 Come on Nemesis, I expected better from you 💀⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":500,"output":329,"cacheRead":50688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51517,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774725082238}}
