{"type":"message","id":"8cd189d1","parentId":"934a60ca","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:58:56.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is saying good morning and wants to start with some good news. Let me search for some good/positive news for today.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Good morning Nemesis! ☀️ Let me find some good vibes for today 🔍"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9f953f1fd5b74ddabdc3e75c","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"good news today March 29 2026 positive uplifting"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":49877,"output":110,"cacheRead":3072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774753131327}}
{"type":"message","id":"13cddc3e","parentId":"8cd189d1","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:59:04.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9f953f1fd5b74ddabdc3e75c","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"good news today March 29 2026 positive uplifting\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 7395,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"92e9c2f8c4c92e22\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHere's a roundup of positive and uplifting news for March 29, 2026:\\n\\n**Medical Breakthroughs and Health:**\\nBiogen has announced encouraging positive results from a Phase 2 trial for litifilimab, a potential new treatment for cutaneous lupus erythematosus (CLE). This marks a significant development, as litifilimab could be the first innovative therapy for CLE in 70 years. The study showed a notable reduction in skin disease activity, offering new hope for those living with the condition.\\n\\n**Global and Community Progress:**\\nOngoing initiatives highlighted in late March 2026 include a global school meal expansion program that now feeds over 200 million children daily, significantly improving attendance, health, and long-term outcomes for millions of families. Additionally, advancements in brain-computer interfaces are helping paralyzed patients regain movement and control robotic limbs, offering profound hope and redefining rehabilitation medicine. The concept of \\\"15-minute cities,\\\" where essentials are within a short walk or bike ride, is also being adopted worldwide, leading to cleaner air, reduced stress, and stronger communities.\\n\\n**Technological Innovations:**\\nEngineers have successfully powered an entire office building without wires using long-range electromagnetic transmission. This breakthrough in wireless electricity has the potential to revolutionize how homes, vehicles, and devices are powered, eliminating cables and improving safety and infrastructure.\\n\\n**Spiritual and Personal Upliftment:**\\nToday, March 29, 2026, marks Palm Sunday, which for Christians signifies the beginning of Holy Week and carries a message of hope, renewal, and spiritual reflection. For those who follow astrology, various horoscopes for March 29, 2026, suggest positive professional news, improved financial health, opportunities for new ventures, and overall personal growth for several zodiac signs.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"92e9c2f8c4c92e22\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/news/6330173\",\n      \"title\": \"taiwannews.com.tw\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hgTAbjeIOjc\",\n      \"title\": \"youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/us/easter-2026-dates-revealed-when-are-good-friday-palm-sunday-and-lent-this-year/articleshow/129863017.cms?from=mdr\",\n      \"title\": \"economictimes.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://news.abplive.com/astro/scorpio-daily-horoscope-march-29-2026-astrological-prediction-day-packed-with-positivity-1833310\",\n      \"title\": \"abplive.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/astrology/horoscope/horoscope-today-daily-astrological-predictions-for-march-29-2026/articleshow/129867430.cms\",\n      \"title\": \"indiatimes.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.hindustantimes.com/astrology/horoscope/weekly-horoscope-aquarius-march-29-april-4-2026-business-may-launch-a-new-venture-101774735704911.html\",\n      \"title\": \"hindustantimes.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"good news today March 29 2026 positive uplifting","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":7395,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92e9c2f8c4c92e22\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere's a roundup of positive and uplifting news for March 29, 2026:\n\n**Medical Breakthroughs and Health:**\nBiogen has announced encouraging positive results from a Phase 2 trial for litifilimab, a potential new treatment for cutaneous lupus erythematosus (CLE). This marks a significant development, as litifilimab could be the first innovative therapy for CLE in 70 years. The study showed a notable reduction in skin disease activity, offering new hope for those living with the condition.\n\n**Global and Community Progress:**\nOngoing initiatives highlighted in late March 2026 include a global school meal expansion program that now feeds over 200 million children daily, significantly improving attendance, health, and long-term outcomes for millions of families. Additionally, advancements in brain-computer interfaces are helping paralyzed patients regain movement and control robotic limbs, offering profound hope and redefining rehabilitation medicine. The concept of \"15-minute cities,\" where essentials are within a short walk or bike ride, is also being adopted worldwide, leading to cleaner air, reduced stress, and stronger communities.\n\n**Technological Innovations:**\nEngineers have successfully powered an entire office building without wires using long-range electromagnetic transmission. This breakthrough in wireless electricity has the potential to revolutionize how homes, vehicles, and devices are powered, eliminating cables and improving safety and infrastructure.\n\n**Spiritual and Personal Upliftment:**\nToday, March 29, 2026, marks Palm Sunday, which for Christians signifies the beginning of Holy Week and carries a message of hope, renewal, and spiritual reflection. For those who follow astrology, various horoscopes for March 29, 2026, suggest positive professional news, improved financial health, opportunities for new ventures, and overall personal growth for several zodiac signs.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92e9c2f8c4c92e22\">>>","citations":[{"url":"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/news/6330173","title":"taiwannews.com.tw"},{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hgTAbjeIOjc","title":"youtube.com"},{"url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/us/easter-2026-dates-revealed-when-are-good-friday-palm-sunday-and-lent-this-year/articleshow/129863017.cms?from=mdr","title":"economictimes.com"},{"url":"https://news.abplive.com/astro/scorpio-daily-horoscope-march-29-2026-astrological-prediction-day-packed-with-positivity-1833310","title":"abplive.com"},{"url":"https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/astrology/horoscope/horoscope-today-daily-astrological-predictions-for-march-29-2026/articleshow/129867430.cms","title":"indiatimes.com"},{"url":"https://www.hindustantimes.com/astrology/horoscope/weekly-horoscope-aquarius-march-29-april-4-2026-business-may-launch-a-new-venture-101774735704911.html","title":"hindustantimes.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774753144165}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7414925","parentId":"13cddc3e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:59:10.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got some good news. Let me compile the best ones for Nemesis.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's some good news to start your Sunday, Nemesis! 🌟\n\n**💊 Medical Win:**\nBiogen just got positive results for a new lupus treatment — the first breakthrough for this disease in **70 years**. Real lives are going to change because of this.\n\n**🌍 200 Million Kids Fed Daily:**\nThe global school meal program now feeds over 200 million children every day. Attendance, health, and long-term outcomes are all improving. Humanity doing humanity things 💛\n\n**⚡ Wireless Electricity Is Real:**\nEngineers just powered an entire office building — wirelessly. No cables. Using long-range electromagnetic transmission. The future is literally here.\n\n**🧠 Brain-Computer Interfaces:**\nParalyzed patients are regaining movement and controlling robotic limbs. What was sci-fi a decade ago is now rehabilitation medicine.\n\n**🏙️ 15-Minute Cities:**\nCities worldwide are being redesigned so everything you need is a 15-minute walk or bike ride. Cleaner air, less stress, stronger communities.\n\nNot bad for a Sunday morning, right? The world's actually doing okay sometimes ☀️\n\nHave a great day Nemesis! ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1057,"output":280,"cacheRead":52928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774753144171}}
