{"type":"message","id":"9ad02123","parentId":"dc20a36d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T03:14:02.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya needs birthday wishes for someone. Let me give her a variety of options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here you go @Sravya! Mix and match depending on who it is 👇\n\n**🎂 Classic & Warm:**\n\"Happy Birthday! 🎉 Wishing you a year filled with love, laughter, and everything that makes you smile. You deserve the best! 🥳💛\"\n\n**✨ Sweet & Thoughtful:**\n\"Happy Birthday to someone who makes the world a little brighter just by being in it. May this year bring you all the happiness you give to others 🌟🎂\"\n\n**😄 Fun & Playful:**\n\"Happy Birthday! 🎈 Another year of being awesome — and you're only getting better with age, like fine wine... or maybe like pizza, because pizza is always good 🍕😂🎉\"\n\n**💫 Inspirational:**\n\"Happy Birthday! 🎊 May this new year of your life be full of new adventures, bold dreams, and moments that take your breath away. The best is yet to come! 🚀✨\"\n\n**💝 For Someone Special:**\n\"Happy Birthday! 💛 Today the world got a little better because you were born. Thank you for being you. Here's to another year of making beautiful memories together 🎂🤗\"\n\n**🔥 Short & Punchy:**\n\"Happy Birthday, legend! 🎉 Stay awesome. Stay you. 🔥\"\n\nWho's it for @Sravya? Friend, crush, family? I can customize it better 😄⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":223,"output":337,"cacheRead":59392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774754034373}}
{"type":"message","id":"578577df","parentId":"9ad02123","timestamp":"2026-03-29T03:16:24.086Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"164\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"163\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 03:16 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Here you go @Sravya! Mix and match depending on who it is 👇\\n\\n🎂 Classic & Warm:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday! 🎉 Wishing you a year filled with love, laughter, and everything that makes you smile. You deserve the best! 🥳💛\\\"\\n\\n✨ Sweet & Thoughtful:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday to someone who makes the world a little brighter just by being in it. May this year bring you all the happiness you give to others 🌟🎂\\\"\\n\\n😄 Fun & Playful:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday! 🎈 Another year of being awesome — and you're only getting better with age, like fine wine... or maybe like pizza, because pizza is always good 🍕😂🎉\\\"\\n\\n💫 Inspirational:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday! 🎊 May this new year of your life be full of new adventures, bold dreams, and moments that take your breath away. The best is yet to come! 🚀✨\\\"\\n\\n💝 For Someone Special:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday! 💛 Today the world got a little better because you were born. Thank you for being you. Here's to another year of making beautiful memories together 🎂🤗\\\"\\n\\n🔥 Short & Punchy:\\n\\\"Happy Birthday, legend! 🎉 Stay awesome. Stay you. 🔥\\\"\\n\\nWho's it for @Sravya? Friend, crush, family? I can customize it better 😄⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nThese are fine\nI will use those \nThan